4040 PRINT "PRESS A KEY TO FIND OUT"
4050 DO : GET K$ : LOOP UNTIL K$<>""
4060 IF GOLD>19 THEN GOTO 4100
4070 PRINT : PRINT "NOPE, THE GUARD HAS KILLED YOU."
